pesticide.PPE: Long sleeved shirt and long pants; Waterproof gloves; Shoes and socks

Safety_Information.general_Info: Harmful if absorbed through skin. Avoid contact with skin, eyes or clothing.
Safety_Information.if_On_Skin: Take off contaminated clothing. Rinse skin immediately with plenty of water for 15-20 minutes. Call a poison control center or doctor for treatment advice.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: This product is a pyrethroid. If large amounts have been ingested, milk, cream and other digestible fats and oils may increase absorption and so should be avoided.
